Introduction

Kang Yuchan, also known as Chan, is a South Korean singer and actor under WAY BETTER. He is the youngest member of the boy group A.C.E and a former member of the project boy group UNB. He made his official debut with A.C.E on May 23, 2017.

In 2017, Chan and fellow A.C.E member Jun competed on KBS 2TV's idol rebooting show The Unit. Chan reached the final lineup by placing 9th, earning a spot in the temporary boy group UNB. The group debuted on April 7, 2018, with the mini-album Boyhood and disbanded in December 2018.

On April 6, 2025 it was announced on Way Better's Official Twitter that he has officially signed with the agency to pursue activities as a solo artist.
